column5: 5 Palms Fish House is located close to Polka-Dot Bikini Beach Boutique, Matagorda Harbor, Salty Dog Liquor Store, Pluggers Bar, Waterfront Restaurant, The Cove Bar, Poco Playa Restaurant and Bar, Riverbend Restaurant, Stanley's Grocery Store and, of course a 5 minute drive to Matagorda's 23 miles of Texas Beach! .
